)V G0(z)V G0(z) + . . .\n\n(27.4)\n\nOr, in matrix representation\n\nG(x x0) = G0(x x0) +\n\nZ\n\nG0(x x2)dx2\u27e8x2 V x1\u27e9dx1G0(x1 x0) + . . .\n\n(27.5)\n\nNote that for the scalar potential \u02c6V = u(\u02c6x) we get\n\nG(x x0) = G0(x x0) +\n\nZ\n\ndx\u2032G0(x x\u2032)u(x\u2032)G0(x\u2032 x0) + . .", "embedding": [-0.05325349, 0.0100701125, 0.036932293, 0.004016206, -0.016537135, -0.021876514, -0.025283141, 0.043151144, -0.04951276, 0.06883376, 0.05710326, 0.0020517472, 0.012450576, -0.001273412, -0.026001448, 0.036376547, 0.010533083, -0.014929026, -0.05741036, 0.013488084, 0.050144173, 0.026100207, -0.046690516, -0.03673339, 0.009792156, 0.026173213, 0.03286093, -0.0011506348, 0.042653974, 0.024826735, 0.016268447, -0.023735635, 0.0144912, -0.036078766, 0.03600862, 0.014471292, -0.007575397, -0.04491089, 0.03946938, -0.017358044, 0.030188676, 0.0282175, 0.006823059, -0.029373033, -0.02683005, 0.0032052055, -0.018197663, 0.027827336, -0.047994137, -0.03540448, 0.010048112, -0.014499392, 0.019860493, -0.05310351, -0.022085208, 0.023648307, 0.002179401, 0.0057520065, -0.015310852, -0.0020473036, 0.010009373, 0.00276445, 0.032296848, 0.0042743883, 0.020402404, 0.045035776, -0.027484147, 0.020405747, 0.04266129, -0.046102162, -0.017986456, -0.028726289, -0.0026667386, 0.024117004, -0.0415215, 0.03935221, 0.017193334, -0.04687724, -0.03359366, -0.019297458, -0.030524742, 0.003940277, -0.053249877, 0.022838552, -0.022642845, -0.008668625, -0.0050546145, 0.026612407, 0.029937748, -0.0010194358, 0.0452716, 0.040430818, 0.016427852, -0.030478792, -0.008839573, 0.033958692, 0.014882866, 0.049687095, 0.03882841, 0.0075593404, -0.0133893965, 0.059528176, -0.018971484, 0.06250316, -0.026617585, 0.039227173, 0.0025648887, 0.029578228, 0.0059990315, -0.07335702, 0.015165771, -0.03306995, 0.037152894, 0.006477782, -0.0049225837, 0.007618613, 0.035656177, -0.015685903, -0.026236877, -0.028226016, 0.022535305, 0.0016503929, 0.038022827, -0.012389959, -0.031662006, -0.002804